videos.description: John Wolford finds Scotty Washington in the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown pass to put Wake Forest ahead 7-3.
videos.headline: Washington gets Wake Forest on the board

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Jerry Howard runs it up the gut for a 2-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Howard dives into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Wake Forest's John Wolford connects with Tabari Hines for 15-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Hines beats his man for catch-and-run TD

videos.description: John Wolford rushes to the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Wake Forest scores third first-half TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech's quarterback TaQuon Marshall runs to the edge for a 49-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Marshall takes it 49 yards to the house on QB keeper

videos.description: Qua Searcy breaks free for a 42-yard touchdown run to give Georgia Tech a 1-point lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Searcy finds an opening for TD run to give Georgia Tech the lead

videos.description: KirVonte Benson runs it up the middle for an 11-yard touchdown run to give Georgia Tech a 31-24 lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Benson runs it up the gut into the end zone

videos.description: Georgia Tech quarterback TaQuon Marshall follows his blockers for a 70-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Marshall's 70-yard TD run seals the win for Georgia Tech

videos.description: Paul Johnson said Georgia Tech didn't make a lot of second-half adjustments, they just made some big plays on offense and defense made big stops.
videos.headline: Johnson:  Georgia Tech 'played like a deer in headlights' in the first half

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall says  tonight's win against Wake Forest gives the Yellow Jackets confidence for next week's match up against Clemson.
videos.headline: Marshall: win gives Georgia Tech confidence
